<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title><%= name %> - Cover Letter</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      margin: 50px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .header {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 0;
    }
    .date {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .recipient {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .salutation,
    .closing {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <p><strong><%= name %></strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="date">
    <p><%= date %></p>
  </div>

  <div class="recipient">
    <p><strong>Hiring Manager</strong></p>
    <p><%= companyName %></p>
  </div>

  <div class="salutation">
    <p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>
  </div>

  <div class="body">
    <p>
      I am writing to express my interest in the <strong><%= jobTitle %></strong> position at <strong><%= companyName %></strong>. With a strong background in <%= skills %>, I am confident in my ability to contribute significantly to your team.
    </p>

    <p>
      Throughout my career, I have achieved the following:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <% achievements.forEach(function(achievement) { %>
        <li><%= achievement %></li>
      <% }); %>
    </ul>

    <p>
      I am particularly impressed by <%= companyName %>'s commitment to innovation and excellence. I believe my experience and passion align well with your company's values and objectives.
    </p>

    <p>
      I would welcome the opportunity to discuss how my skills and experiences can benefit <%= companyName %>. Thank you for considering my application.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="closing">
    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0;"><%= name %></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
